# scitex-agentic-journal — example environment.
#
# Copy to `.env` (or export inline) and edit the values you actually
# need. Lines beginning with `#` are documentation only; this file is
# checked into git, the real `.env` is not.
#
# The package itself reads no env vars at runtime today; the SCITEX_*
# vars below are scaffold knobs read by the CLI and the (not-yet-shipped)
# Gate-1 orchestrator. They are documented here so the PS-129 audit
# rule can confirm every `SCITEX_AGENTIC_JOURNAL_*` token referenced in
# `src/` has a discoverable description.

# Path to an alternate YAML config for the CLI / orchestrator. When
# unset, the CLI falls back to `./config.yaml`, then to
# `~/.scitex/agentic-journal/config.yaml`.
# SCITEX_AGENTIC_JOURNAL_CONFIG=/abs/path/to/config.yaml
